snippet.textDisplay: The girl dancing can't hear or express her views verbally; but she can feel the music; according to me, she is very lucky indeed to attain the actual ESSENCE OF MUSIC which we, having all our sense organs responding perfectly can never ever reach so deep like the way she does; her dancing steps could never have been so dynamic if she doesn't feel the music; I salute this COMPLETE ARTIST who has easily been the INSPIRATION not only for the 'Handicapped' people but for the whole women fraternity. THANKS to all the crew members of this wonderful presentation.🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻
